// HistoryToolbar
// Toolbar row shown at the top of the document editor for version history
// navigation. Shows current version indicator, prev/next arrows, and a revert
// button when viewing a historical version.

FUNCTION HistoryToolbar(currentIndex, totalVersions, onPrev, onNext, onRevert, onClose) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Displays "Version X of Y" label.
  Prev/Next arrows disabled at boundaries.
  Revert button calls onRevert for the currently previewed version.
  Close/back button calls onClose to exit history mode.
